snippet.title: Double Fine Presents: Everything by David OReilly - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Everything is out now on PS4 !
Steam (PC & Mac) coming Apr 21st - Wishlist it now - http://store.steampowered.com/app/582270

http://www.everything-game.com
